  Stable on alpha, bug #320733

  30 Jun 2010; Pawel Hajdan jr <phajdan.jr@gentoo.org> rubygems-0-r2.ebuild:
  x86 stable wrt bug #320733

  29 Jun 2010; Christoph Mende <angelos@gentoo.org> rubygems-0-r2.ebuild:
  Stable on amd64 wrt bug #320733

  10 Jun 2010; Jeroen Roovers <jer@gentoo.org> rubygems-0-r2.ebuild:
  Stable for HPPA (bug #321153).

  23 May 2010; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> rubygems-0-r2.ebuild:
  Drop ruby19 support to facilitate upcoming stabilization.

  01 May 2010; Alex Legler <a3li@gentoo.org> rubygems-0.ebuild,
  rubygems-0-r1.ebuild, rubygems-0-r2.ebuild, rubygems-0-r3.ebuild:
  dev-lang/ruby:1.9 no longer provides rubygems

*rubygems-0-r3 (03 Apr 2010)

